FBIS3-52580 "drnes004_l_94001" FBIS-NES-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 ISRAEL `Great Importance' Seen in Damascus Statement TA0601055394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0500 GMT 6 Jan 94 TA0601055394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Well-informed Israeli sources attribute great importance to a statement made by a Radio Damascus commentator that in exchange for a withdrawal from all the occupied territories, Israel will reap the fruits of peace on all fronts, without exception. Our political correspondent Shlomo Raz reports that according to these sources, this is the first statement of its kind. They believe it was made in anticipation of the Clinton-al-Asad summit.
